00:58:16,539 --> 00:58:18,039
Tunjukkan dirimu.

993
00:58:18,479 --> 00:58:21,910
Hei, di mana kamu? Hei.

994
00:58:21,910 --> 00:58:23,279
- Tidak.
- Berani-beraninya kamu

995
00:58:23,279 --> 00:58:25,749
- bersembunyi di rumah Soo Il.
- Dia terdengar marah.

996
00:58:25,749 --> 00:58:27,120
Tunggu sampai aku menemukanmu.

997
00:58:27,420 --> 00:58:30,489
Kamu di mana? Di mana kamu bersembunyi?

998
00:58:35,529 --> 00:58:37,989
Hai, Geum Byung. Ini aku, Chun Sim.

999
00:58:37,989 --> 00:58:39,600
- Hei.
- Astaga.

1000
00:58:39,830 --> 00:58:41,830
Dasar wanita jalang!

1001
00:58:43,569 --> 00:58:45,670
Tidak ada yang bisa kamu lakukan

1002
00:58:45,670 --> 00:58:48,640
- selain mencuri pasangan teman?
- Kak.

1003
00:58:48,640 --> 00:58:50,569
Kakak harus berhenti.

1004
00:58:50,569 --> 00:58:51,840
Hei, kamu.

1005
00:58:51,840 --> 00:58:54,640
Akan kubunuh kamu dan aku akan bunuh diri setelahnya.

1006
00:58:54,640 --> 00:58:56,350
Kak, hentikan!

1007
00:58:56,350 --> 00:58:57,479
Menyingkir dari kakak.

1008
00:58:58,180 --> 00:59:00,950
Beraninya kamu. Kamu sudah gila?

1009
00:59:01,080 --> 00:59:02,850
Aku akan membunuhmu.

1010
00:59:02,850 --> 00:59:05,759
Dasar wanita keji. Akan kubunuh kamu hari ini.

1011
00:59:05,759 --> 00:59:08,160
- Wanita licik.
- Kak! Mari kita bicarakan.

1012
00:59:08,160 --> 00:59:09,930
Kamu kira kakak mau bicara?

1013
00:59:09,930 --> 00:59:13,430
Kamu kira kamu istrinya Soo Il?

1014
00:59:13,430 --> 00:59:16,999
Apa hakmu menyetrika bajunya?

1015
00:59:16,999 --> 00:59:19,900
Beraninya kamu berganti pakaian di sini dan meninggalkan pakaianmu.

1016
00:59:19,900 --> 00:59:21,709
Selamatkan aku.

1017
00:59:21,709 --> 00:59:23,170
- Kak.
- Kenapa kamu...

1018
00:59:23,170 --> 00:59:25,709
- Ibu...
- Minggir.

1019
00:59:25,880 --> 00:59:27,279
Kemari kamu.

1020
00:59:27,279 --> 00:59:28,749
Menyingkir.

1021
00:59:28,749 --> 00:59:30,549
- Jangan.
- Awas.

1022
00:59:38,789 --> 00:59:40,120
Hai, Do Ran.

1023
00:59:41,519 --> 00:59:42,630
Apa?

1024
00:59:44,430 --> 00:59:45,600
Apa?

1025
00:59:45,600 --> 00:59:48,430
Ayah, cepat kemari. Sekarang juga.

1026
00:59:48,430 --> 00:59:51,600
Baik, ayah akan segera ke sana.

1027
00:59:52,200 --> 00:59:53,340
Apa ada masalah?

1028
00:59:53,340 --> 00:59:55,440
Aku harus pulang sebentar.

1029
00:59:58,209 --> 01:00:00,140
Ada apa dengannya belakangan ini?

1030
01:00:02,049 --> 01:00:04,209
Bisakah kamu minggir?

1031
01:00:04,209 --> 01:00:06,049
Chun Sim, sini keluar.

1032
01:00:06,049 --> 01:00:08,489
- Kak, hentikan.
- Wanita licik.

1033
01:00:08,489 --> 01:00:11,120
Ada pria lain di luar sana.

1034
01:00:11,120 --> 01:00:15,160
Bagaimana bisa kamu mengincar pria yang disukai temanmu?

1035
01:00:15,160 --> 01:00:16,630
Keluar dari sini!

1036
01:00:16,989 --> 01:00:18,700
- Minggir.
- Do Ran.

1037
01:00:19,130 --> 01:00:20,729
- Nyonya Park.
- Hei.

1038
01:00:20,860 --> 01:00:23,229
Kenapa Anda seperti ini? Tenanglah.

1039
01:00:23,469 --> 01:00:25,769
Soo Il.

1040
01:00:26,469 --> 01:00:28,610
Chun Sim masuk sendiri

1041
01:00:28,610 --> 01:00:30,809
seperti pencuri di malam hari

1042
01:00:30,809 --> 01:00:34,840
dan meletakkan bunga di vas serta menyetrika bajumu.

1043
01:00:34,840 --> 01:00:38,350
Itu namanya penerobosan.

1044
01:00:38,350 --> 01:00:40,749
Kamu harus melaporkannya ke polisi.

1045
01:00:41,279 --> 01:00:44,049
- Nyonya Park, aku...
- Soo Il.

1046
01:00:44,049 --> 01:00:46,590
Wanita licik. Kemari.

1047
01:00:47,090 --> 01:00:48,190
Lepaskan kakak.

1048
01:00:48,190 --> 01:00:51,029
Menyingkirlah dari Soo Il.

1049
01:00:51,029 --> 01:00:53,999
- Jangan bersembunyi di belakangnya.
- Nyonya Park.

1050
01:00:53,999 --> 01:00:57,499
- Aku mengizinkannya
- Lepaskan.

1051
01:00:57,499 --> 01:00:59,200
masuk kemari.

1052
01:01:00,069 --> 01:01:01,340
Apa?

1053
01:01:02,640 --> 01:01:04,809
Kamu mengizinkannya?

1054
01:01:06,180 --> 01:01:07,410
Ya.

1055
01:01:07,680 --> 01:01:09,350
Maaf.

1056
01:01:11,209 --> 01:01:12,979
Pak Kan dan aku...

1057
01:01:13,549 --> 01:01:14,580
Kami

1058
01:01:15,049 --> 01:01:17,090
saling mencintai.

1059
01:01:17,090 --> 01:01:20,289
Apa? Kalian saling mencintai?

1060
01:01:21,289 --> 01:01:22,590
Soo Il.

1061
01:01:23,459 --> 01:01:26,459
Kamu dan Chun Sim

1062
01:01:27,059 --> 01:01:28,830
kini tinggal bersama?

1063
01:01:29,330 --> 01:01:30,969
Begitu?

1064
01:01:35,870 --> 01:01:36,870
Ya.

1065
01:01:38,269 --> 01:01:39,910
Pak Kang!

1066
01:01:40,279 --> 01:01:43,509
Teganya kamu bersikap sekejam ini kepadaku.

1067
01:01:43,509 --> 01:01:46,019
Teganya kamu melakukan ini kepadaku.

1068
01:01:46,019 --> 01:01:49,150
Pak Kang.

1069
01:01:52,090 --> 01:01:53,789
Pak Kang.

1070
01:01:59,229 --> 01:02:00,360
Nyonya Park.

1071
01:02:01,200 --> 01:02:02,299
Maaf.

1072
01:02:04,729 --> 01:02:05,870
Geum Byung.

1073
01:02:06,900 --> 01:02:09,239
Tolong biarkan kami saling mencintai.

1074
01:02:10,410 --> 01:02:11,670
Kumohon.

1075
01:02:12,080 --> 01:02:13,180
Kami

1076
01:02:13,840 --> 01:02:16,209
sungguh saling menyukai.

1077
01:02:16,209 --> 01:02:18,249
Kami tidak terpisahkan sekarang.

1078
01:02:19,819 --> 01:02:23,090
Geum Byung, aku sebenarnya sudah mencoba

1079
01:02:23,190 --> 01:02:26,059
kembali ke Amerika untuk putus dengannya.

1080
01:02:26,989 --> 01:02:28,059
Tapi

1081
01:02:28,690 --> 01:02:31,559
aku langsung kembali sebelum sempat naik pesawat.

1082
01:02:31,590 --> 01:02:33,999
Aku tidak bisa hidup tanpa Pak Kang.

1083
01:02:34,900 --> 01:02:36,499
Maaf, Geum Byung.

1084
01:02:36,499 --> 01:02:37,969
Kamu sungguh-sungguh?

1085
01:02:38,870 --> 01:02:39,900
Ya.

1086
01:02:40,799 --> 01:02:42,539
Kamu temanku.

1087
01:02:42,539 --> 01:02:44,840
Tidak bisakah kamu memahaminya?

1088
01:02:45,209 --> 01:02:46,509
Pak Kang.

1089
01:02:47,809 --> 01:02:49,580
Kamu sungguh menyukai Chun Sim?

1090
01:02:49,580 --> 01:02:51,309
Sepenuh hatimu?

1091
01:02:52,850 --> 01:02:55,390
Ya, maaf.

1092
01:02:56,890 --> 01:02:58,150
Baik.

1093
01:02:59,019 --> 01:03:02,360
Lantas, hiduplah bahagia.

1094
01:03:03,489 --> 01:03:05,259
- Ya...
- Kak.

1095
01:03:07,330 --> 01:03:09,069
Ayah, aku akan bicara nanti.

1096
01:03:09,969 --> 01:03:12,140
Kak!

1097
01:03:15,969 --> 01:03:17,309
Pak Kang.

1098
01:03:33,890 --> 01:03:35,019
Hong Shil.

1099
01:03:35,019 --> 01:03:37,190
Saat kudengar Hong Joo kembali ke Amerika,

1100
01:03:37,190 --> 01:03:39,459
