1148
01:05:37,380 --> 01:05:39,350
Baik, tentu saja.

1149
01:05:40,019 --> 01:05:41,249
Besok?

1150
01:05:41,950 --> 01:05:43,819
Baiklah kalau begitu.

1151
01:05:43,819 --> 01:05:45,519
Sampai jumpa besok.

